  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Empowering innovative teachers in Latin America</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">FIDAL seeks to promote innovative teaching practices to improve quality of education in Latin America.  We seek to empower primary and secondary teachers from formal and non-formal education sector through an annual Education Excellence Contest that will recognize 20 innovative educational actions leaded by teachers in and out of class.  FIDAL will achieve this goal by granting these teachers: scholarships, exchange programs, educational materials, books, and visibility in the region.</narrative>
  </description>
